history.content:
CS169 will be open today for enrollment -sometime between 4:20P and 7P.   Through Friday, it will be senior cs/eecs majors only. On Saturday (Aug 10) all CS/EECS majors will be able to enroll to the extent space is still available (and junior majors already on the waitlist will be moved in first). Discussion sections will be scheduled by the end of today but students will sign up for "999" section so that specific discussion section you end up attending can be based on your whole team's availability.

See @9874 for more information.
history.subject: CS 169 will open for enrollment today
